precis:
Transfer to the Minister of INDUSTRY, SCIENCE and TECHNOLOGY of all the
powers, duties and functions of the Minister of Employment and Immigration
with respect to regional economic development in the Province of Quebec, as
well as the control and supervision of that portion of the public service
known as the FEDERAL OFFICE OF REGIONAL DEVELOPMENT - QUEBEC.
